room_title: Escape room "Diamond Heist" by The Heist Escape Room in San Jose
review: I was never a fan of escape rooms and "team building" but this one changed my mind. My heart was racing up until the end. Great job with this one guys!

room_title: Escape room "Diamond Heist" by The Heist Escape Room in San Jose
review: I am a big fan of escape rooms, and I'm happy to have found one right here in Fremont! For a business that's just starting out, they're doing an awesome job. Come check it out; you won't be disappointed. Our group did not make it out but can't wait to go back and try it again!

room_title: Escape room "Diamond Heist" by The Heist Escape Room in San Jose
review: This was my first escape room. I had gone with a big group and we all had a lot of fun. I would definitely recommend.
